{"tid":2099890,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"在英持有BNO者未必可以在英申請新簽証，申請都有可能被拒，日期不詳","createTime":"2020-07-08T15:02:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T01:49:47.000Z","uid":22054,"like":10,"dislike":107,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"255c55635ac86bc36f071c51f0425052082770dd","tid":2099890,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T15:02:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hongkongwatch.org/legal-faq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongwatch.org%2Flegal-faq&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDK1gnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=6311c6e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongwatch.org/legal-faq</a><br />\n<br />\nYou are not automatically eligible for the 5-year limited leave to remain (LLR). You have to first go through an application process, and <span style=\"color: red;\">there is no guarantee of success.</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWhat if you choose to arrive in the UK using this 6-month stay (i.e. before the BNO Measures are in force)? The UK Government has indicated that BNO holders in the UK <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">may</span></strong> be allowed to apply under the BNO Measures for a specified period of time. It should be noted that this is an indication only, and <span style=\"color: red;\">there is no guarantee that this will indeed be permitted and catered</span> for in the final BNO Measures.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbeb305394acc136ceddfc724747fd89e1b07655","tid":2099890,"uid":78947,"like":4,"dislike":27,"score":-23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T15:03:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aadb9d61e3c1b26cad3a51b2181953d33a2cdb6","tid":2099890,"uid":20170,"like":101,"dislike":2,"score":99,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T15:06:19.000Z","msg":"點解呢排咁多標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一係fake標題，一係講一半唔講一半嚟誤導人<br />\n拉"},{"pid":"f6b7a6d1